                            <handNote>Black majuscule letters against ochre background. Delta is formed with a lambda on a horizontal bar; mu with the central strokes reminiscent of an upsilon on a stem and surmounted by a dot; tau with a small dot added to its stem at mid-height; omega with its apex surmounted by a crosslet;  ΟΥ joined in ligature. Middle dot after Παντάνασσα. Double point after ψυχῆς, δίκης, ὑσχυρίων. Accents and breathings systematic, with errors. A cross with rays between the cross-arms marks the beginning and the end of the text. Two pseudo-Kufic decorative elements at the end of the inscription.
